{
  "stem": "1765.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were arrested, put on trucks, sent on the trucks to the railroad station, and put into cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents and my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at the station, my grandfather was separated from us, and put in a different echelon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what it's called.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These trains were called echelons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my grandmother shrieked and carried on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was just so relieved that my father wasn't taken that I'm-- you know, I am not prettifying things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I tell it as I remember it from my child's point of view.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was so relieved that my father was with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were put in this cattle car with about 30 or 35 other people, and we traveled for six weeks to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as we were leaving our house on the truck, people were crying and lamenting and carrying on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Musik's mother and his sister were by the truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My grandmother was there-- my mother's mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they had it so much worse, because they remained in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Germans came, and they were put in ghettos, And they were killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Musik's sister and mother were killed during the first few months of German occupation by being sent to Ponar, which was-- it's one of the five places [INAUDIBLE], which is a memorial killing woods.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And everybody lamented our going to Siberia, but it would-- would've been wonderful if everyone was sent to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother's brother came to the door-- Liusik-- to see what was going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the doorbell rang, and my mother was told by the soldier to open it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she opened it and there was Liusik.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember where I sat.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
